data.description: Beautiful North Maury County farm just off the highly desirable Carters Creek Pike. Lovingly cared for custom build one level ranch home, large shop, horse barn, fenced and cross fenced, pond,gorgeous sunrises and sunsets, a perfect second build site, vegetable gardens and fruit trees.  This type of property is hard to find!  Ready for your family with 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, updated kitchen, huge pantry and mud room, plus a perfect space for a mother in law quarters.  Location! 20 minutes to Franklin, 10 minutes to Spring Hill. All of the conveniences of the city - High Speed Internet, Door Dash, etc without the congestion.  Two dividable (after purchase) lots combined to make almost 16 acres in the greenbelt and over the 15 are thresh hold for tax savings.This is a combination of Tracts 023 010.23 & Tract 023    010.02 to make almost 16 Acres.
